Package com.aston.group.stationdefender.screens

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameScreen
    This screen holds the main game loop
    IntroScreen
    IntroScreen is the first screen shown in the game and contains the game title and buttons that link to other screens such as the background information screen, instruction screen etc.
    MenuScreen
    MenuScreen is the screen shown when pressing the menu button from within the game.
    TwoTextScreen
    TwoTextScreen is a class that creates a screen holding a title text, a body of text, a back button and an optional continue button.
